===Speak with Guangda{{subst:void|<!--202090101-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Exalting Sanctum|The duties of the Realm-Keeping Commission's orderlies are like bricks, to be moved wherever they are needed. The work of Guangda is not an easy one, and now he is worrying in front of the Realm-Keeping Commission chancery...<br />Out of goodwill, you can ask him if he needs help, but whether you will help is a different matter...}}
